text: David Ramírez may refer to: * David Ramírez (footballer, born 1981), Argentine football midfielder * David Ramírez (footballer, born 1993), Costa Rican football forward * David Noel Ramírez Padilla (born 1950), dean of the Monterrey Institute of Technology * David Ramirez (editor), American film and television editor * David Ramirez (musician), American musician from Austin, Texas
